'''福克-{}-兰群岛'''（{{lang-en|Falkland Islands}}），[[阿根廷|阿根廷]]称'''马尔维-{}-纳斯群岛'''（{{lang-es|Islas Malvinas}}），是位于南[[大西洋|大西洋]]巴塔哥尼亚大陆棚的[[群岛|群岛]]。主岛地处[[南美洲|南美洲]][[巴塔哥尼亚|巴塔哥尼亚]]南部海岸以东约500公里，[[纬度|南纬]]52°左右海域。整个群岛包括[[东福克兰岛|东福克兰岛]]、[[西福克兰岛|西福克兰岛]]和776个小岛，总面积12,200[[平方公里|平方公里]]。福克兰群岛是[[英国海外领土|英国海外领土]]，拥有[[地方分权|内部自治权]]，[[英国|英国]]负责其国防和外交事务。群岛首府是[[斯坦利_(福克兰群岛)|斯坦利]]，位于东福克兰岛。

福克兰群岛的发现及其后欧洲人殖民统治的历史均有争议。[[法兰西殖民帝国|法国]]、[[大不列颠王国|英国]]、[[西班牙帝国|西班牙]]和[[阿根廷邦联|阿根廷]]都曾在岛上设立定居点。英国于1833年重申了其殖民统治，但此后的阿根廷历届政府仍宣称拥有岛上[[主权|主权]]。1982年，阿根廷对岛上实施军事占领，[[福克蘭戰爭|福克蘭戰爭]]由此爆发，之后阿根廷战败撤军，英国再次拥有群岛。

根据2012年的人口普查结果，除卻服役军人及其家眷，福克兰群岛一共有2,932位居民<ref name="census2012">{{cite web |url=http://www.falklands.gov.fk/assets/Headline-Results-from-Census-2012.pdf |title=Falkland Islands Census 2012: Headline results |date=2012-09-10 |publisher=Falkland Islands Government |accessdate=2012-12-19 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130520184434/http://www.falklands.gov.fk/assets/Headline-Results-from-Census-2012.pdf |archivedate=2013-05-20 }}</ref>，其中大部分都是具英国血统的福克兰群岛人。其他种族包括[[法国人|法国人]]、[[直布罗陀人|直布罗陀人]]和[[斯堪的纳维亚|斯堪的纳维亚人]]。来自英国、南大西洋[[圣赫勒拿岛|圣赫勒拿岛]]和[[智利|智利]]的[[移民|移民]]已经扭转岛上人口数量下降的趋势。群岛的主要和官方语言都是[[英语|英语]]，根据《{{link-en|1983年英国国籍（福克兰群岛）法令|British Nationality (Falkland Islands) Act 1983}}》，福克兰群岛人都是合法的[[英国国籍法|英国公民]]。

群島坐落在[[海洋性气候|亚寒带和温带海洋性气候]]地区边界，两个主要岛屿上都拥有海拔高度达到700米的山脉。岛上有大量[[鸟类|鸟类]]种群，但由于有外来物种的竞争，有许多种鸟类已经不再在主岛繁衍。群岛的主要经济活动包括[[渔业|渔业]]、[[旅游业|旅游业]]和以高品质羊毛出口为重心的绵羊养殖业。由于与阿根廷存在海上争端，由福克兰群岛政府许可的石油勘探仍然有争议。

== 词源 ==
福克兰群岛的名称源于[[福克兰海峡|福克兰海峡]]，该[[海峡|海峡]]将[[东福克兰岛|东]][[西福克兰岛|西福克兰]]二岛分隔开来<ref name="Jones">{{cite book | last = Jones | first = Roger | title = What's Who? A Dictionary of Things Named After People and the People They are Named After | year = 2009 | publisher = Matador | location = Leicester, England | page = 73 | isbn = 978-1-84876-047-9}}</ref>。[[英格兰王国|英国]]探险队于1690年来到群岛，船长约翰·斯特朗（{{lang|en|John Strong}}）以这次旅程的赞助人、[[海軍司庫|海軍司庫]]{{link-en|第五代福克兰子爵安东尼·卡里|Anthony Cary, 5th Viscount of Falkland}}来为海峡命名<ref name="Dotan-2010">{{cite book | last = Dotan | first = Yossi | title = Watercraft on World Coins: America and Asia, 1800–2008 | volume=2 | year = 2010 | publisher = The Alpha Press | location = Portland, Oregon | isbn = 978-1-898595-50-2 | page = 165}}</ref><ref name="Room-2006">{{cite book | last = Room | first = Adrian | title = Placenames of the World | url = https://archive.org/details/placenamesofworl02edroom | edition=2nd | year = 2006 | publisher = McFarland & Company, Inc. | location = Jefferson, North Carolina | isbn = 978-0-7864-2248-7 | page = [https://archive.org/details/placenamesofworl02edroom/page/129 129]}}</ref>。子爵的头衔又是来源于[[苏格兰|苏格兰]]{{link-en|福克兰法夫|Falkland, Fife}}，小镇的英文名称“{{lang|en|Falkland}}”源于“{{lang|en|folkland}}”，意思是通过民间权利拥有的土地<ref name="Room-2006" />。不过这个名称正式应用到群岛则要到1765年，[[大不列颠王国|不列颠]][[英国皇家海军|皇家海军]]船长{{link-en|约翰·拜伦|John Byron}}代表[[乔治三世_(英国)|乔治三世]]宣布群岛为“福克兰群岛”，“福克兰”也成为群岛的标准简称<ref name="Paine-2000">{{cite book | last = Paine | first = Lincoln | title = Ships of Discovery and Exploration | url = https://archive.org/details/shipsofdiscovery0000pain | year = 2000 | publisher = Mariner Books | location = New York | isbn = 978-0-395-98415-4 | page = [https://archive.org/details/shipsofdiscovery0000pain/page/45 45]}}</ref><ref name="Room-2006" />。

群岛的西班牙语名称“马尔维纳斯群岛”（{{lang|es|Islas Malvinas}}）是由法语“{{lang|fr|Îles Malouines}}”衍生而来，[[法兰西王国|法国]]探险家[[路易斯·安东尼·布干维尔|路易斯·安东尼·布干维尔]]于1764年以此为群岛命名<ref name="Hince-2001">{{cite book | last = Hince | first = Bernadette | title = The Antarctic Dictionary | year = 2001 | publisher = CSIRO Publishing | location = Collingwood, Melbourne | isbn = 978-0-9577471-1-1}}</ref>{{rp|121}}。布干维尔的船队是从[[圣马洛|圣马洛港]]出发，所以他將岛上创立的第一个定居点命名為圣马洛<ref name="Hince-2001" />{{rp|121}}<ref name="Room-2006" />。而位于法国西部[[布列塔尼半岛|布列塔尼半岛]]的圣马洛港则是源于该市创建者、[[基督教|基督教]]{{le|马洛 (圣人)|Malo (saint)|同名}}[[传福音|福音传教士]]<ref name="Balmaceda-2011">{{cite book | last = Balmaceda | first = Daniel | chapter = 36 | title = Historias Inesperadas de la Historia Argentina | year = 2011 | publisher = Editorial Sudamericana | location = Buenos Aires | isbn = 978-950-07-3390-8}}</ref>。

联合国第四委员会在第20届[[联合国大会|联合国大会]]上作出决定，除[[西班牙语|西班牙语]]外，所有其他语种的联合国文献都将把该领地称为“福克兰群岛（马尔维纳斯）”（{{lang|en|Falkland Islands (Malvinas)}}），西班牙语文献则称为“马尔维纳斯群岛（福克兰群岛）”（{{lang|es|Islas Malvinas (Falkland Islands)}}）<ref name="Foreign-Office-1961">{{cite book | author = Foreign Office | title = Report on the Proceedings of the General Assembly of the United Nations | year = 1961 | publisher = H.M. Stationery Office | location = London | page = 80}}</ref>。联合国用于统计处理用途的名称则是“福克兰群岛（马尔维纳斯）”（{{lang|en|Falkland Islands (Malvinas)}}）<ref name="std_name">{{cite web | archivedate = 2014-06-28 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140628144412/http://unstats.un.org/unsd/methods/m49/m49alpha.htm | deadurl = no | url = http://unstats.un.org/unsd/methods/m49/m49alpha.htm | title = Standard Country and Area Codes Classifications | publisher = United Nations Statistics Division | date = 2013-02-13 | accessdate = 2014-07-23 }}</ref>。

===中文名稱===
[[中華民國|中華民國]]官方直接承認其屬於英國，對「福克蘭群島」一名並無異議<ref>{{cite web| title = 福克蘭群島| url = https://www.boca.gov.tw/sp-foof-countrycp-03-226-52b7e-04-1.html| work = | quote = 福克蘭群島是英國海外領地| publisher = [[中華民國外交部|中華民國外交部]]領事事務局| date = | accessdate = | language = zh-tw| archive-date = 2021-03-20| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210320061525/https://www.boca.gov.tw/sp-foof-countrycp-03-226-52b7e-04-1.html| dead-url = no}}</ref>，台灣的媒體<ref>{{Cite web|title=福克蘭群島淪陷 通報首起新冠肺炎確診病例|url=https://money.udn.com/money/story/5599/4467871|accessdate=2020-07-15|last=經濟日報|work=經濟日報|language=zh-TW|archive-date=2021-03-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210320061453/https://money.udn.com/money/story/5599/4467871|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web| title = 馬拉度納請求「上帝之手」再現　消滅新冠肺炎| url = https://sports.ettoday.net/news/1702819?redirect=1| work = | publisher = 東森新聞雲| quote = 由於英、阿才剛發生福克蘭群島戰爭，引起極大爭議。| accessdate = 2020-05-01| archive-date = 2021-03-20| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210320061517/https://sports.ettoday.net/news/1702819?redirect=1| dead-url = no}}</ref>、教科書與民間發行的世界地圖<ref>{{cite book |title=最新世界地圖　中華民國建國百年紀念首版 |date=2011-02 |publisher=上河文化 |location=台北 |url=http://www.sunriver.com.tw/images/relief/relief_018b2.jpg |accessdate=2020-04-30 |archive-date=2017-06-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170615050258/http://www.sunriver.com.tw/images/relief/relief_018b2.jpg |dead-url=no }}</ref>亦然，因此民間大多不知「馬爾維納斯群島」這個稱呼。

[[中華人民共和国|中華人民共和国]]官方部分支持阿根廷对该群岛的主权声索。历史上，中华人民共和国的地图和年鉴在1950至1960年代一直只用“福克兰”的名称，[[文革|文革]]期间为了表示「对[[拉丁美洲|拉丁美洲]]国家的支持」，用括号加上了“马尔维纳斯群岛”，1982年后改用后者为正式名称，将“福克兰群岛”用括号加注，一般简称“马岛”<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://news.cntv.cn/special/thinkagain/falklandislands/index.shtml|title=马岛，两个多世纪的领土争议|website=中国网络电视台评论频道|accessdate=2021-03-20|archive-date=2021-03-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210320061454/https://s.go-mpulse.net/boomerang/N3GAX-LCNLN-FQTF6-PZ6TT-3G33E|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2014年2月11日，[[国家测绘地理信息局|国家测绘地理信息局]]地理信息与地图司公布《关于在公开地图上表示有关国家和地区的通知》（国测图发〔2014〕1号），规定“马尔维纳斯群岛”统一标注为“'''马尔维纳斯群岛（阿根、英争议）（英称福克兰群岛）'''”，地图标注之外的文字说明部分可适当简化。首府“阿根廷港（斯坦利港）”改为“阿根廷港（斯坦利）”<ref name="报道0213A">{{cite web |author1=国家测绘地理信息局地理信息与地图司 |title=关于在公开地图上表示有关国家和地区的通知（国测图发〔2014〕1号） |url=https://www.zrzyst.cn/gfxwj/326.jhtml |website=自然资源部地图资源审查中心 |accessdate=2022-02-13}}</ref>。

== 历史 ==
虽然来自[[巴塔哥尼亚|巴塔哥尼亚]]的[[火地群岛|火地群岛]]土著居民有可能早在史前时代就到达过福克兰群岛<ref>{{cite journal |author=G. Hattersley-Smith |date=1983-06 |title=Fuegian Indians in the Falkland Islands |journal=Polar Record |volume=21 |issue=135 |pages=605–606 |publisher=Cambridge University Press |doi=10.1017/S003224740002204X |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131106032411/http://journals.cambridge.org/action/displayAbstract%3Bjsessionid%3DC6D4151001DCF6AE8937B936C8FDCC62.journals?fromPage=online&aid=5400340 |archivedate=2013-11-06 |deadurl=no |url=http://journals.cambridge.org/action/displayAbstract;jsessionid=C6D4151001DCF6AE8937B936C8FDCC62.journals?fromPage=online&aid=5400340 |accessdate=2014-07-23 }}</ref>，但到欧洲人发现群岛时，这里仍然荒无人烟<ref name="Carafano-2005">{{cite book | last = Carafano | first = James Jay | chapter = Falkland/Malvinas Islands | title = Britain and the Americas: Culture, Politics, and History | year = 2005 | editor = Will Kaufman | editor2 = Heidi Slettedahl Macpherson | publisher = ABC-CLIO | location = Santa Barbara, California | isbn = 978-1-85109-431-8}}</ref>{{rp|367}}。早在16世纪末时就开始有探险家声称自己发现了这片群岛，但对于这些早期探险家发现的究竟就是福克兰群岛还是南大西洋的其它岛屿这点仍未达成一致<ref name="M White">{{cite news | author = Michael White | title = Who first owned the Falkland Islands? | newspaper = The Guardian | publisher = Guardian News and Media | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131104212314/http://www.theguardian.com/uk/blog/2012/feb/02/who-first-owned-falkland-islands | url = http://www.theguardian.com/uk/blog/2012/feb/02/who-first-owned-falkland-islands? | date = 2012-02-02 | accessdate = 2014-07-23 | archivedate = 2013-11-04 }}</ref><ref name="Goebel-1971">{{cite book | last = Goebel | first = Julius | title = The Struggle for the Falkland Islands: A Study in Legal and Diplomatic History | url = https://archive.org/details/struggleforfalkl0000goeb_v6k7 | year = 1971 | publisher = Kennikat Press | location = Port Washington, New York | isbn = 978-0-8046-1390-3}}</ref>{{rp|xiv–xv}}{{#tag:ref|[[历史学家|历史学家]][[约翰·邓莫尔|约翰·邓莫尔]]（{{lang|en|John Dunmore}}）经过对福克兰群岛发现史的分析后总结认为：西班牙、[[荷兰|荷兰]]、英国，甚至[[意大利|意大利]]和[[葡萄牙|葡萄牙]]都有探险家声称发现这片群岛，不过最后两个国家的说法可信度比较低。<ref name="Dunmore-2005">{{cite book | last = Dunmore | first = John | title = Storms and Dreams | year = 2005 | publisher = Exisle Publishing Limited | location = Auckland, New Zealand | isbn = 978-0-908988-57-0}}</ref>{{rp|93}}|group="注"}}。1690年，英国船长约翰·斯壮途经[[秘鲁|秘鲁]]和[[智利|智利]]近海到达群岛并发现了福克兰海峡，他还记录了岛上的水域和野生动物，这也是存在文献记载证实的人类第一次登陆该群岛<ref name="Gustafson-1988">{{cite book | last = Gustafson| first = Lowell | title = The Sovereignty Dispute Over the Falkland (Malvinas) Islands | url = https://archive.org/details/sovereigntydispu0000gust| year = 1988 | publisher = Oxford University Press | location = New York | isbn = 978-0-19-504184-2}}</ref>{{rp|5}}<ref name="Headland-1989">{{cite book | last = Headland | first = Robert | title = Chronological List of Antarctic Expeditions and Related Historical Events | year = 1989 | publisher = Cambridge University Press | location = New York | isbn = 978-0-521-30903-5 | page = 66}}</ref><ref name="Heawood-2011">{{cite book | last = Heawood | first = Edward | title = A History of Geographical Discovery in the Seventeenth and Eighteenth Centuries | year = 2011 | edition = Reprint | editor = F.H.H. Guillemard | publisher = Cambridge University Press | location = New York | isbn = 978-1-107-60049-2 | page = 182}}</ref>。

1764年，法国船长路易斯·安东尼·布干维尔在东福克兰岛建立了{{link-en|路易港（福克兰群岛）|Port Louis, Falkland Islands}}（{{lang|en|Port Louis}}），福克兰群岛开始有人类居住。1766年，英国船长{{link-en|约翰·麦克布赖德|John MacBride (Royal Navy officer)}}（{{lang|en|John MacBride}}）也在[[森德尔斯岛|森德尔斯岛]]建立了{{link-en|埃格蒙特港|Port Egmont}}（{{lang|en|Port Egmont}}）{{#tag:ref|1764年，布士维尔宣布群岛属于[[路易十五|路易十五]]；1765年，英国船长约翰·拜伦宣布群岛属于英王乔治三世<ref name="Gustafson-1988" />{{rp|9-10}}<ref name="Dunmore-2005" />{{rp|139-140}}。|group="注"}}。不过，历史学家对各定居点的居民是否知晓另一个定居点存在仍未达成一致意见<ref name="Goebel-1971" />{{rp|226, 232, 269}}<ref name="Gustafson-1988" />{{rp|9-10}}。1766年，西班牙获得了法国在岛上建立的定居点，并于次年将其更名为{{link-es|索莱达港|Puerto Soledad}}（{{lang|es|Puerto Soledad}}）<ref name=Segal-1991>{{cite book | last = Segal | first = Gerald | title = The World Affairs Companion | url = https://archive.org/details/worldaffairscomp00sega | year = 1991 | publisher = Simon & Schuster/Touchstone | location = New York | isbn = 978-0-671-74157-0 | page = [https://archive.org/details/worldaffairscomp00sega/page/240 240]}}</ref>。西班牙人发现埃格蒙特港后于1770年将其占领，引发了{{link-en|1770年福克兰群岛危机|Falklands Crisis (1770)}}，[[大不列颠王国|大不列颠王国]]和西班牙之间的战争如箭在弦，但最终西班牙于1771年将埃格蒙特港归还英国，战争得以避免<ref name="Gibran-1998">{{cite book | last = Gibran | first = Daniel | title = The Falklands War: Britain Versus the Past in the South Atlantic | url = https://archive.org/details/falklandswarbrit0000gibr | year = 1998 | publisher = McFarland & Company, Inc. | location = Jefferson, North Carolina | isbn = 978-0-7864-0406-3}}</ref>{{rp|26}}。

英国和西班牙人建立的定居点在群岛上共存到1774年，英国出于新的经济和战略考量主动从群岛撤军，乔治三世对福克兰群岛的主权主张名存实亡<ref name="Gibran-1998" />{{rp|26-27}}。西班牙的[[拉普拉塔总督辖区|拉普拉塔总督辖区]]成为领地上仅有的政府存在。西福克兰岛处于荒废，索莱达港基本上成了战俘营<ref name="Gibran-1998" />{{rp|27}}。欧洲爆发[[拿破仑战争|拿破仑战争]]期间，英国试图夺取拉普拉塔总督辖区，1806年，群岛总督撤离，剩下的西班牙殖民地驻军也在1811年跟进，只剩[[高乔人|高乔人]]和渔民自愿留了下来<ref name="Gibran-1998" />{{rp|27}}。

此后十余年间，只有渔船才偶尔来到这片群岛，其政治地位也没有什么争议。但到了1820年，为[[拉普拉塔联合省|拉普拉塔联合省]]工作的美国[[私掠|私掠者]]{{link-en|大卫·朱伊特|David Jewett}}（{{lang|en|David Jewett}}）[[上校|上校]]告知锚定船只，[[布宜诺斯艾利斯|布宜诺斯艾利斯]]已于1816年宣布继承这片南大西洋西班牙殖民地的主权<ref name="Gibran-1998" />{{rp|27}}<ref name="Marley-2008">{{cite book | last = Marley | first = David | title = Wars of the Americas | url = https://archive.org/details/warsamericaschro00marl | year = 2008 | publisher = ABC-CLIO | location = Santa Barbara, California | edition = 2nd | isbn = 978-1-59884-100-8 | page = [https://archive.org/details/warsamericaschro00marl/page/n714 714]}}</ref>{{#tag:ref|阿根廷法律分析师罗伯特·拉沃尔（{{lang|en|Roberto Laver}}）称，英国当时没有理睬朱伊特，因为他所代表的政府“当时不受英国或其他任何其他国家承认”，并且“在声称拥有主权后也不存在任何的占领行动”<ref name="Laver-2001">{{cite book | last = Laver | first = Roberto | title = The Falklands/Malvinas Case | year = 2001 | publisher = Martinus Nijhoff Publishers | location = The Hague | isbn = 978-90-411-1534-8}}</ref>{{rp|73}}。|group="注"}}。由于群岛上没有永久居民，布宜诺斯艾利斯于1823年授权德国出生的商人{{link-en|路易斯·韦尔内|Luis Vernet}}（{{lang|en|Luis Vernet}}）在这里捕鱼并获取野牛{{#tag:ref|前往福克兰群岛前，韦尔内为自己的授权许可争取到了英国领事馆的印章，并且到1828年布宜诺斯艾利斯延长许可后又重复了这样的做法<ref name="Cawkell-2001">{{cite book | last = Cawkell | first = Mary | title = The History of the Falkland Islands | year = 2001 | publisher = Anthony Nelson Ltd. | location = Oswestry, England | isbn = 978-0-904614-55-8}}</ref>{{rp|48-50}}。他和领事馆之间有着良好的关系，因此期望英国重新取得群岛时，[[英国政府|其政府]]会一并保护他的移民点<ref name="Cawkell-2001" />{{rp|50}}。|group="注"}}。韦尔内于1826年在索莱达港遗址定居，然后逐渐积累资源，直到足以带来更多的定居者，形成永久性的殖民地<ref name="Gibran-1998" />{{rp|27-28}}<ref name="Sicker-2002">{{cite book | last = Sicker | first = Martin | title = The Geopolitics of Security in the Americas | year = 2002 | publisher = Praeger Publishers | location = Westport, Connecticut | isbn = 978-0-275-97255-4 | page = 32}}</ref>。1829年，布宜诺斯艾利斯任命韦尔内为群岛军事和民事的总指挥<ref name="Pascoe-Pepper-2008">{{cite book | last1 = Pascoe | first1 = Graham | last2 = Pepper | first2 = Peter | chapter = Luis Vernet | title = The Dictionary of Falklands Biography (Including South Georgia): From Discovery Up to 1981 | editor = David Tatham | publisher = David Tatham | location = Ledbury, England | year = 2008 | isbn = 978-0-9558985-0-1}}</ref>{{rp|540-546}}，他则试图经过规管，阻止外来船只捕杀鲸鱼和海豹的活动<ref name="Gibran-1998" />{{rp|27}}。韦尔内的事业起初还算顺利，但到了1831年，因在捕捞权和狩猎权上出现争议，美国砲艦“{{le|列星頓號砲艦|USS Lexington (1825)|列星頓號}}”（{{lang|en|USS Lexington}}）对岛上定居点进行了突击搜查<ref name="Pascoe-Pepper-2008" />{{rp|541-544}}{{#tag:ref|“列克星敦号”的日志记载该船只毁掉了军火和一间商店，但韦尔内声称整个定居点都被摧毁，并以此向美国政府索赔<ref name="Pascoe-Pepper-2008" />{{rp|541-544}}。|group="注"}}，[[美国海军|美国海军]]将领{{link-en|西拉斯·邓肯|Silas Duncan}}（{{lang|en|Silas Duncan}}）宣布岛上的政府统治到此结束<ref name="Peterson-1964">{{cite book | last = Peterson | first = Harold | title = Argentina and the United States 1810–1960 | year = 1964 | publisher = University Publishers Inc. | location = New York | isbn = 978-0-87395-010-7 | page = 106}}</ref>。
[[File:Edward_Gennys_Fanshawe,_Mount_William,_Falkland_Islands,_May_1849_(Portion_B).png|left]]

布宜诺斯艾利斯试图通过派遣驻军保持对定居点的影响力，但在1832年的兵变发生后，英军于次年到达群岛，重申英国拥有这里的主权<ref name="Graham-Yooll-2002">{{cite book | last = Graham-Yooll | first = Andrew | title = Imperial Skirmishes: War and Gunboat Diplomacy in Latin America | year = 2002 | publisher = Signal Books Limited | location = Oxford, England | isbn = 978-1-902669-21-2}}</ref>{{rp|50}}。以布宜诺斯艾利斯省長[[胡安·曼努埃尔·德·罗萨斯|胡安·曼努埃尔·德·罗萨斯]]为首的[[阿根廷邦联|阿根廷邦联]]抗议英国的这一做法<ref name="Reginald-Elliot-1983">{{cite book | last1 = Reginald | first1 = Robert |  last2 = Elliot | first2 = Jeffrey | title = Tempest in a Teapot: The Falkland Islands War | year = 1983 | publisher = Whitehall Co. | location = Wheeling, Illinois | isbn = 978-0-89370-267-0}}</ref>{{rp|25-26}}{{#tag:ref|正如罗伯特·拉沃尔所说的那样，罗萨斯并没有因这一事件断绝与英国的外交关系，因为“英国的经济支持”“至关重要”；不过，他把福克兰群岛作为筹码，希望能取消阿根廷欠下英国[[霸菱银行|霸菱银行]]的数百万英镑债务<ref name="Laver-2001" />{{rp|122-123}}。1850年，罗萨斯的政府同英国缔造条约，“结束了存在的分歧，恢复了（两国间）完美的友谊”<ref name=Hertslet-1851>{{cite book | last = Hertslet | first = Lewis | title = A Complete Collection of the Treaties and Conventions, and Reciprocal Regulations, At Present Subsisting Between Great Britain and Foreign Powers, and of the Laws, Decrees, and Orders in Council, Concerning the Same | year = 1851 | publisher = Harrison and Son | location = London | volume = 8 | page = 105}}</ref>。|group="注"}}，阿根廷从此还开始不间断地针对英国提出正式抗议<ref name="Gustafson-1988" />{{rp|34-35}}{{#tag:ref|阿根廷先后在1841、1849、1884、1888、1908、1927和1933年举行了抗议活动，并且自1946年起每年都会在联合国抗议<ref name="Gustafson-1988" />{{rp|34}}。|group="注"}}。英国军队完成自己的使命后就离开了领地，群岛基本上变成“无人地带”<ref name="Graham-Yooll-2002" />{{rp|51-52}}。韦尔内的副手，苏格兰人{{link-en|马修·布里斯班|Matthew Brisbane}}（{{lang|en|Matthew Brisbane}}）同年返回群岛试图试图恢复韦尔内的事业，但是，[[高乔人|高乔人]]{{link-en|安东尼奥·里韦罗|Antonio Rivero}}（{{lang|en|Antonio Rivero}}）在一片动荡的路易港带领其他多位“心怀不满的人士”[[谋杀|谋杀]]了布里斯班和定居点的多位领导人，幸存者躲到了附近小岛的一个山洞，直到英国人返回并恢复秩序<ref name="Graham-Yooll-2002" />{{rp|51-52}}。1840年，福克兰群岛成为[[英國殖民地|皇家殖民地]]，苏格兰定居者随后建立了正式的教會牧區<ref name="Aldrich-Connell-1998">{{cite book | last1 = Aldrich | first1 = Robert | last2 = Connell | first2 = John | title = The Last Colonies | url = https://archive.org/details/lastcolonies00aldr | year = 1998 | publisher = Cambridge University Press | location = New York | isbn = 978-0-521-41461-6 | page = [https://archive.org/details/lastcolonies00aldr/page/201 201]}}</ref>。四年后，几乎所有居民都迁到了杰克逊港，认为这里更适合作为政府的所在地，商人塞缪尔·拉冯（{{lang|en|Samuel Lafone}}）开始鼓励英国将群岛殖民化<ref name="Bernhardson-2011">{{cite book | last = Bernhardson| first = Wayne| title = Patagonia: Including the Falkland Islands | year = 2011 | publisher = Friesens | location = Altona, Manitoba | isbn = 978-1-59880-965-7 | chapter = Stanley and Vicinity: History}}</ref><ref name="Reginald-Elliot-1983" />{{rp|9, 27}}。

杰克逊港不久后更名为[[斯坦利_(福克兰群岛)|斯坦利]]，并在1845年正式成为政府所在地<ref name="Reginald-Elliot-1983" />{{rp|9}}。斯坦利早期曾因船运货物丢失导致声誉不佳，只有在紧急情况下，船只才会绕过[[合恩角|合恩角]]停在该港口<ref name="Bernhardson-2011" />。不过，事实证明，福克兰群岛的地理位置对船舶维修来说非常理想，并且很适合进行销售和购买沉船及其上货物的“沉船贸易”<ref name="Strange-1987">{{cite book | last = Strange | first = Ian | title = The Falkland Islands and Their Natural History | url = https://archive.org/details/falklandislands00stra | year = 1987 | publisher = David & Charles | location = Newton Abbot, England | isbn = 978-0-7153-8833-4}}</ref>{{rp|72-74}}。除了这些行业外，群岛的商业活动较少，因为牧场中野牛的皮革附加价值很低。1851年，{{link-en|福克兰群岛公司|Falkland Islands Company}}收购了拉冯日落西山的产业{{#tag:ref|由于拉冯未能成功建立任何永久性的定居点，并且在提供给定居点的牛肉价格上存在分歧，殖民政府和拉冯之间的关系一直很紧张。此外，他的特许状要求拉冯从英国带人前来定居，但他带来的大部分却都是来自[[乌拉圭|乌拉圭]]的高乔人<ref name="Strange-1987" />{{rp|84}}。|group="注"}}，然后成功地引进了用于羊毛养殖业的{{link-en|切维厄特绵羊|Cheviot sheep}}，带动其他养殖场纷纷效仿，群岛上的经济开始有了起色<ref name="Bernhardson-2011" /><ref name="Reginald-Elliot-1983" />{{rp|9}}。由于进口材料的成本很高，加上劳动力不足及由此产生的薪酬成本过高，船舶维修业开始失去竞争力。1870年以后，南美洲煤炭的低价加剧了蒸汽船取代帆船的步伐，群岛上的船舶维修业因此前景黯淡；到了1914年[[巴拿马运河|巴拿马运河]]开通时，岛上的这一行当很快就成了历史<ref name="Strange-1987" />{{rp|72-73}}。1881年，福克兰群岛从经济上与英国独立<ref name="Reginald-Elliot-1983" />{{rp|9}}。超过一个世纪的时间里，福克兰群岛公司从与英国的羊毛贸易中获益匪浅，公司主宰了群岛的贸易和就业，并且拥有斯坦利的大部分房屋<ref name="Bernhardson-2011" /><ref name="Reginald-Elliot-1983" />{{rp|9}}。
[[File:Battle_of_the_Falkland_Islands,_1914.jpg|left]]

20世纪的前50年里，福克兰群岛在英国对[[亚南极|亚南极]]岛屿和[[南极洲|南极洲]]一部分的领土主张中起到了重要作用。福克兰群岛从1908年起将这些领土作为[[福克兰群岛属土|福克兰群岛属土]]进行管辖，直到1985年这些地区成为[[南乔治亚和南桑威奇群岛|南乔治亚岛与南桑威奇群岛]]时止<ref name="Day-2013">{{cite book | last = Day | first = David | title = Antarctica: A Biography | edition = Reprint | year = 2013 | publisher = Oxford University Press | location = Oxford, England | isbn = 978-0-19-967055-0 | pages = 129-130}}</ref>。福克兰群岛还成为英国控制南大西洋的辅助军事基地，在两次世界大战中都起到了一定作用。[[第一次世界大战|一战]]期间，[[福克蘭群島海戰|福克蘭群島海戰]]于1914年12月爆发，一支皇家海军舰队战胜了[[德意志帝国|德意志帝国]]的一支分遣舰队。到了[[第二次世界大战|二战]]时期，[[埃克塞特号重巡洋舰_(约克级)|埃克塞特号重巡洋舰]]在1939年12月的[[拉普拉塔河口海战|拉普拉塔河口海战]]中受损，因此前往福克兰群岛进行修理<ref name="Carafano-2005" />{{rp|367}}。1942年，由于担心领地被[[大日本帝国|日本]]侵占，一个原定前往[[印度|印度]]的营重新部署到了福克兰群岛作为驻军<ref name="Haddelsey-Carroll-2014">{{cite book | last1 = Haddelsey | first1 = Stephen | last2 = Carroll | first2 = Alan | title = Operation Tabarin: Britain's Secret Wartime Expedition to Antarctica 1944–46 | year = 2014 | publisher = The History Press | location = Stroud, England | isbn = 978-0-7509-5511-9 | chapter = Prologue}}</ref>。战争结束后，福克兰群岛的经济受到羊毛价格下降的影响，同时英国和阿根廷对群岛主权的纠纷死灰复燃，由此导致的政治不稳定也对经济产生了负面影响<ref name="Bernhardson-2011" />。

20世纪下半叶，阿根廷总统[[胡安·裴隆|胡安·裴隆]]声称对群岛拥有主权，英国和阿根廷之间的关系日趨緊張<ref name="Zepeda-2005">{{cite book | last = Zepeda | first = Alexis | chapter = Argentina | title = Britain and the Americas: Culture, Politics, and History | year = 2005 | editor = Will Kaufman | editor2 = Heidi Slettedahl Macpherson | publisher = ABC-CLIO | location = Santa Barbara, California | isbn = 978-1-85109-431-8}}</ref>{{rp|102}}。60年代期间，联合国通过了一项[[非殖民化|非殖民化]]的决议案，阿根廷认为这一决议案对自己的立场有利，两国间的主权争端于是愈演愈烈<ref name="Laver-2001" />{{rp|125}}。1965年，联合国大会通过第2065号决议案，呼吁两国展开双边谈判，以和平手段解决争端<ref name="Laver-2001" />{{rp|125}}。1966年至1968年，英国就移交福克兰群岛同阿根廷进行秘密谈判，认为群岛居民会接受这样的安排<ref name="Thomas-1991">{{cite book | last = Thomas | first = David | title = The View from Whitehall | url = https://archive.org/details/towardresolution0000unse | encyclopedia = Toward Resolution? The Falklands/Malvinas Dispute| editor = Wayne Smith | publisher = Lynne Rienner Publishers | location = Boulder, Colorado | year=1991 | isbn = 978-1-55587-265-6}}</ref>{{rp|24}}。1971年，双方就群岛和大陆间的贸易关系达成协议，阿根廷因此于1972年在斯坦利建成了一座临时机场<ref name="Reginald-Elliot-1983" />{{rp|9}}。然而，福克兰群岛居民对此提出了异议，并通过强力游说[[英国国会|英国议会]]表明了立场，再加上英国和阿根廷的紧张关系，双方的谈判一直冻结到了1977年<ref name="Thomas-1991" />{{rp|24-27}}。

1979年，[[撒切尔夫人|撒切尔夫人]]当选[[英国首相|英国首相]]，由于政府面临预算削减，而维持对福克兰群岛的统治又需要一定的费用，英国再次考虑将群岛主权移交阿根廷<ref name="Guardian">{{cite news | archivedate = 2013-10-29 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131029194820/http://www.theguardian.com/uk/2005/jun/28/falklands.past | deadurl = no | url = http://www.theguardian.com/uk/2005/jun/28/falklands.past | title = UK held secret talks to cede sovereignty: ''Minister met junta envoy in Switzerland, official war history reveals'' | newspaper = The Guardian | publisher = Guardian News and Media | date = 2005-06-28 | accessdate = 2014-07-23 | author = Richard Norton-Taylor and Rob Evans }}</ref>。实质性的主权谈判在1981年再度中止，双方的争端随时间的推移持续升级<ref name="Thomas-1991" />{{rp|28-31}}。1982年4月，阿根廷入侵福克兰群岛和[[南乔治亚和南桑威奇群岛|英国在南大西洋的其他领地]]，分歧升级成了[[马岛战争|武装冲突]]，两个多月后，英国远征军重新夺回了包括福克兰群岛在内的所有领地<ref name="Reginald-Elliot-1983" />{{rp|5, 10-12, 67}}<ref name="Zepeda-2005" />{{rp|102-103}}。战争结束后，英国扩充了军力，增加了群岛的驻军规模，还建成了[[芒特普莱森特皇家空军基地|芒特普莱森特皇家空军基地]]<ref name="Gibran-1998" />{{rp|130-135}}。这场战争还遗留下了117片雷区，其中包含有近两万枚车辆和人员杀伤地雷<ref name = "BBC_Mines">{{cite news | url = http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/americas/8564061.stm | title = The Long Road to Clearing Falklands Landmines | author = <!--Staff writer(s); no by-line.--> | date = 2010-03-14 | newspaper = BBC News | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140715060252/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/americas/8564061.stm | deadurl = no | publisher = British Broadcasting Corporation | accessdate = 2014-07-23 | archivedate = 2014-07-15 }}</ref>。由于出现了大量伤亡，初步排雷作业于1983年中止<ref name = "BBC_Mines" />{{#tag:ref|雷区都围了起来并做出标记，其中仍有未引爆的炸药和简易爆炸装置<ref name = "BBC_Mines" />。实践证明，福克兰群岛的地雷清除工作非常困难，因为有一些地雷是经空投放置，还有一些并不在标记出的雷区内，约80%位于沙子或泥炭下，地雷在这样的地层中可能会移动，增大移除工作的困难和风险<ref>{{cite journal | last = Ruan | first = Juan Carlos | last2 = Macheme | first2 = Jill E. | date = 2001-08 | title = Landmines in the Sand: The Falkland Islands | url = http://www.jmu.edu/cisr/journal/5.2/focus/falklands.htm | journal = The Journal of ERW and Mine Action | publisher = James Madison University | volume = 5 | issue = 2 | issn = 1533-6905 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140714164355/http://www.jmu.edu/cisr/journal/5.2/focus/falklands.htm | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2014-07-14 | accessdate = 2014-07-23 }}</ref>。|group="注"}}。

根据[[欧内斯特·沙克尔顿|沙克尔顿勳爵]]的建议，福克兰群岛的经济活动从以绵羊为基础的单一养殖业发展成渔业、[[旅游业|旅游业]]和绵羊养殖业的混合产业，群岛上还建立了[[专属经济区|专属经济区]]<ref name="Cawkell-2001" />{{rp|147}}{{#tag:ref|1976年时，沙克尔顿勳爵就完成了一份有关群岛经济前景的报告，但当时的英国政府为避免与阿根廷在群岛主权上正面冲突而没有落实报告中的建议<ref name="Cawkell-2001" />{{rp|147}}。沙克尔顿勳爵于1982年再度获命对领地经济发展提供报告。他在新报告中批评了多家大型养殖企业，并建议把养殖场的所有权由在外土地所有人转交给当地土地所有人。沙克尔顿还提出了经济多元化的建议，发展渔业、石油勘探和旅游业。此外，他还提议建设道路网络，并通过保护措施保护群岛的自然资源。<ref name="Cawkell-2001" />{{rp|147}}|group="注"}}。原有的道路网络得到拓展，快活岭空军基地的建成也让岛上可以起降长途航班<ref name="Cawkell-2001" />{{rp|147}}。石油勘探也已启动，并且有迹象显示福克兰群岛盆地有望开展商业开采<ref>{{cite news | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140714161035/http://en.mercopress.com/2014/05/15/falklands-drilling-will-resume-in-second-quarter-of-2015-announced-premier-oil | archivedate = 2014-07-14 | url = http://en.mercopress.com/2014/05/15/falklands-drilling-will-resume-in-second-quarter-of-2015-announced-premier-oil | title = Falklands Drilling Will Resume in Second Quarter of 2015, Announced Premier Oil | author = <!--Staff writer(s); no by-line.--> | date = 2014-05-15 | newspaper = MercoPress | accessdate = 2014-07-23 }}</ref>。2009年，英国根据《[[渥太华条约|渥太华条约]]》中规定的义务开始再度展开地雷清除工作，到了2012年，萨伯山区域的地雷已经清除，这一拥有历史里程碑意义的地区得以在30年来首次对外界开放<ref>{{cite news | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130117054208/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/picturegalleries/worldnews/9169829/The-Falkland-Islands-30-years-after-the-war-with-Argentina.html?frame=2178743 | archivedate = 2013-01-17 | url = http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/picturegalleries/worldnews/9169829/The-Falkland-Islands-30-years-after-the-war-with-Argentina.html?frame=2178743 | title = The Falkland Islands, 30 Years After the War with Argentina | author = <!--Staff writer(s); no by-line.--> | newspaper = Daily Telegraph | publisher = Telegraph Media Group | accessdate = 2014-07-23 }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | author = Grant Munro | date = 2011-12-08 | newspaper = MercoPress | accessdate = 2014-07-23 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140714162622/http://en.mercopress.com/2011/12/08/falklands-land-mine-clearance-set-to-enter-a-new-expanded-phase-in-early-2012 | archivedate = 2014-07-14 | deadurl = no | url = http://en.mercopress.com/2011/12/08/falklands-land-mine-clearance-set-to-enter-a-new-expanded-phase-in-early-2012 | title = Falklands' Land Mine Clearance Set to Enter a New Expanded Phase in Early 2012 }}</ref>。1990年，阿根廷和英国重新建立了外交关系，但由于无法对未来主权讨论的条款达成一致，双边关系自重建以来就在不断恶化<ref name="Lansford-2012">{{cite book | last = Lansford | first = Tom | title = Political Handbook of the World 2012 | year = 2012 | editor = Thomas Muller | editor2 = Judith Isacoff | editor3 = Tom Lansford | publisher = CQ Press | location = Los Angeles, California | isbn = 978-1-60871-995-2 | page = 1528}}</ref><ref name="Zepeda-2005" />{{rp|102-103}}。两国政府间的纠纷已经导致“一些分析师预测，由于近期福克兰群岛周边水域捕鱼业的扩张……阿根廷和英国之间的利益冲突将日益加剧”<ref name="Zepeda-2005" />{{rp|103}}。

== 政府 ==
[[File:Falkland_Islands_-_Governor's_House.jpg|thumb]]的总督府是[[福克兰群岛总督|福克兰群岛总督]]的[[官邸|官邸]]所在]]
福克兰群岛属自治[[英国海外领土|英国海外领土]]<ref name="Cahill-2010">{{cite book | last = Cahill | first = Kevin | title = Who Owns the World: The Surprising Truth About Every Piece of Land on the Planet | url = https://archive.org/details/whoownsworldsurp00cahi | year = 2010 | publisher = Grand Central Publishing | location = New York | isbn = 978-0-446-55139-7 | chapter = Falkland Islands}}</ref>。根据2009年通过的[[宪法|宪法]]，群岛拥有充分的内部自治权，英国只负责外交和军事事务，保留军事力量“保护英国利益并确保领地整体上得到良好治理”<ref name="Constitution">{{cite news | title = New Year begins with a new Constitution for the Falklands | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131029192759/http://en.mercopress.com/2009/01/01/new-year-begins-with-a-new-constitution-for-the-falklands | url = http://en.mercopress.com/2009/01/01/new-year-begins-with-a-new-constitution-for-the-falklands | deadurl = no | newspaper = MercoPress | date = 2009-01-01 | accessdate = 2014-07-23 | archivedate = 2013-10-29 }}</ref>。[[英国君主|英国君主]]是[[国家元首|国家元首]]，[[福克兰群岛总督|福克兰群岛总督]]代表君主行使[[行政机构|行政权力]]，他还可以根据立法议员的建议任命[[福克兰群岛行政长官|行政长官]]<ref name="constitutiontext">{{cite web | archivedate = 2014-07-09 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140709031954/http://www.legislation.gov.uk/uksi/2008/2846/pdfs/uksi_20082846_en.pdf | url = http://www.legislation.gov.uk/uksi/2008/2846/pdfs/uksi_20082846_en.pdf | title = The Falkland Islands Constitution Order 2008 | publisher = The Queen in Council | date = 2008-11-05 | accessdate = 2014-07-23 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。总督和行政长官都是[[政府首脑|政府首脑]]<ref name="Buckman-2012">{{cite book | last = Buckman | first = Robert | title = Latin America 2012 | url = https://archive.org/details/isbn_9781610488877 | year = 2012 | publisher = Stryker-Post Publications | location = Ranson, West Virginia | isbn = 978-1-61048-887-7 | page = [https://archive.org/details/isbn_9781610488877/page/394 394]}}</ref>。现任总督科林·罗伯茨于2014年4月获得任命<ref>{{cite news | title = Falklands Governor Colin Roberts takes office next Tuesday 29 April | newspaper = MercoPress | date = 2014-04-28 | accessdate = 2014-07-23 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140429190742/http://en.mercopress.com/2014/04/28/falklands-governor-colin-roberts-takes-office-next-tuesday-29-april | archivedate = 2014-04-29 | deadurl = no | url = http://en.mercopress.com/2014/04/28/falklands-governor-colin-roberts-takes-office-next-tuesday-29-april }}</ref>，现任行政长官基思·帕吉特则是在2012年3月得到委任<ref>{{cite news | title = Keith Padgett, first Falklands' government CE recruited in the Islands | url = http://en.mercopress.com/2012/03/07/keith-padgett-first-falklands-government-ce-recruited-in-the-islands | newspaper = MercoPress | date = 2012-03-07 | accessdate = 2014-07-23 | archivedate = 2013-10-29 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131029200231/http://en.mercopress.com/2012/03/07/keith-padgett-first-falklands-government-ce-recruited-in-the-islands | deadurl = no }}</ref>。英國現任主管福克兰群岛事務的官員是[[雨果·施维尔|雨果·施维尔]]，他负责管理英国有关群岛的外交政策<ref>{{cite web | title = Minister of State at the Foreign & Commonwealth Office | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140701085522/https://www.gov.uk/government/ministers/minister-of-state--14 | deadurl = no | url = https://www.gov.uk/government/ministers/minister-of-state--14 | publisher = United Kingdom Government | date = 2014-06-27 | accessdate = 2014-07-23 | archivedate = 2014-07-01 }}</ref>。

总督根据群岛{{link-en|福克兰群岛行政局|Executive Council of the Falkland Islands}}（{{lang|en|Executive Council of the Falkland Islands}}）的建议行事，行政局由行政长官、财政總監和三名从立法议会中选出的议员组成，並由总督担任主席<ref name="constitutiontext" />。立法会议采用[[一院制|一院制]]，其中包括行政长官、财政部长和八名议员，这八名议员经[[普选|普选]]产生，任期四年，其中五名来自斯坦利，三名来自其他地区<ref name="constitutiontext" />。福克兰群岛上不存在[[政党|政党]]，所有政治家都[[无党籍|无党籍]]<ref>{{cite book | author = [[中央情报局|Central Intelligence Agency]] | title = The CIA World Factbook 2012 | year = 2011 | publisher = Skyhorse Publishing, Inc. | location = New York | isbn = 978-1-61608-332-8 | chapter = Falkland Islands (Malvinas) – Government}}</ref>。从{{link-en|2013年福克兰群岛普选|Falkland Islands general election, 2013}}开始，立法议员成為受薪工作，并且需要全职从事议会的工作，放弃之前的任何工作职位或商业利益<ref>{{cite news | title = Falklands lawmakers: "The full time problem" | date = 2013-10-28 | accessdate = 2014-07-23 | url = http://en.mercopress.com/2013/10/28/falklands-lawmakers-the-full-time-problem | newspaper = MercoPress | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131029213124/http://en.mercopress.com/2013/10/28/falklands-lawmakers-the-full-time-problem | archivedate = 2013-10-29 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。

在[[英國脫歐|英國脫歐]]前，福克兰群岛曾經因为与英国之间的联系而成为[[欧洲联盟|欧洲联盟]][[欧洲联盟特别领域|海外国家和地区]]的一份子<ref>{{cite web |url=http://ec.europa.eu/europeaid/where/octs_and_greenland/index_en.htm |title=EU relations with Overseas Countries and Territories |date=2014-06-04 |author=EuropeAid |publisher=European Commission |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140701021720/http://ec.europa.eu/europeaid/where/octs_and_greenland/index_en.htm |deadurl=yes |archivedate=2014-07-01 |accessdate=2014-07-23 }}</ref>。群岛的司法系统主要沿襲[[英国法律|英国法律]]，受[[外交及联邦事务部|外交及联邦事务部]]监督<ref name="Sainato-2010">{{cite book | last = Sainato | first = Vincenzo | editor= Graeme Newman | editor2 = Janet Stamatel | editor3 = Hang-en Sung | chapter = Falkland Islands | title = Crime and Punishment around the World | volume = 2 | year = 2010 | publisher = ABC-CLIO | location = Santa Barbara, California | isbn = 978-0-313-35133-4 | pages = 157-158}}</ref>，宪法中还将领地与《[[欧洲人权公约|欧洲人权公约]]》的各项原则相结合<ref name="Constitution" />。居民有权上诉至[[欧洲人权法院|欧洲人权法院]]和[[英国枢密院|英国枢密院]]<ref>{{cite web | location = London | accessdate = 2014-07-23 | page = 4 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131029191402/https://www.gov.uk/government/uploads/system/uploads/attachment_data/file/217278/british-overseas-territories.pdf | archivedate = 2013-10-29 | year = 2012 | deadurl = no | url = https://www.gov.uk/government/uploads/system/uploads/attachment_data/file/217278/british-overseas-territories.pdf | title = A New Approach to the British Overseas Territories | publisher = Ministry of Justice }}</ref><ref>{{cite legislation UK | type = si | year = 2006 | number = 3205 | si = The Falkland Islands (Appeals to Privy Council) (Amendment) Order 2009}}</ref>。{{link-en|皇家福克兰群岛警察|Royal Falkland Islands Police}}负责执法<ref name="Sainato-2010" />，对群岛的[[福克兰群岛军事|军事防御]]则由英国提供<ref>{{cite book | author = Central Intelligence Agency | title = The CIA World Factbook 2012 | year = 2011 | publisher = Skyhorse Publishing, Inc. | location = New York | isbn = 978-1-61608-332-8 | chapter = Falkland Islands (Malvinas) – Transportation}}</ref>。群岛上有英国军队驻守，福克兰群岛政府还提供资金组建了一个额外的[[连|连]]级[[轻装步兵|轻装步兵]]部队，称为{{link-en|福克兰群岛国防军|Falkland Islands Defence Force}}<ref name="timesfidf">{{cite news | url = http://www.timesonline.co.uk/tol/news/world/us_and_americas/article7052002.ece | title = Falklands Defence Force better equipped than ever, says commanding officer | date = 2010-03-06 | author = Martin Fletcher | newspaper = The Times | publisher = News UK | accessdate = 2011-03-18 | archive-date = 2020-05-11 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200511114151/http://www.thetimes.co.uk/ | dead-url = no }}</ref>。根据《[[联合国海洋法公约|联合国海洋法公约]]》，福克兰群岛领海从其沿海基线向外延伸200[[海里|海里]]（相当于370公里），但这一边界与阿根廷的海上边界出现了重叠<ref>{{cite web | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131208020111/https://www.dur.ac.uk/ibru/resources/south_atlantic/ | archivedate = 2013-12-08 | url = https://www.dur.ac.uk/ibru/resources/south_atlantic/ | title = Argentina and UK claims to maritime jurisdiction in the South Atlantic and Southern Oceans | author = International Boundaries Research Unit | publisher = Durham University | accessdate = 2014-07-23 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。

=== 主权争议 ===
英国和阿根廷都声称拥有福克兰群岛的主权，被列入联合国[[非自治领土|非自治领土]]名单<ref name="Br"/>。英国的立场是：福克兰群岛的人民没有表现出变革的意愿，并且不存在任何有关群岛且悬而未决的问题<ref name="Lansford-2012" /><ref>{{cite news | archivedate = 2013-11-04 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131104212352/http://www.theguardian.com/uk/2009/mar/28/falkland-islands-sovereignty-argentina | url = http://www.theguardian.com/uk/2009/mar/28/falkland-islands-sovereignty-argentina | author = Nicholas Watt | title = Falkland Islands sovereignty talks out of the question, says Gordon Brown | newspaper = The Guardian | publisher = Guardian News and Media | date = 2009-03-27 | accessdate = 2014-07-23 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。英国这些立场源于其自1833年起对群岛的持续管理（仅有1982年阿根廷短暂占领群岛期间例外），并且岛上居民“根据《[[联合国宪章|联合国宪章]]》拥有自决权”<ref>{{cite web | publisher = United Kingdom Foreign & Commonwealth Office and Ministry of Defence | work = Policy | url = https://www.gov.uk/government/policies/supporting-the-falkland-islanders-right-to-self-determination | title = Supporting the Falkland Islanders' right to self-determination | date = 2013-03-12 | accessdate = 2014-07-23 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140325033113/https://www.gov.uk/government/policies/supporting-the-falkland-islanders-right-to-self-determination | archivedate = 2014-03-25 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。阿根廷方面政策坚持认为，福克兰群岛人没有自决的权利，声称英国在1833年以“更强大的武力”威胁驱逐了群岛上的阿根廷当局和居民，并且从此以后禁止阿根廷人民到群岛上定居<ref name="RIS" /><ref>{{cite journal | author = Michael Reisman | date = 1983-01 | title = The Struggle for The Falklands | journal = Yale Law Journal | volume = 93 | issue = 287 | page = 306 | publisher = Faculty Scholarship Series | accessdate = 2013-10-23 | url = http://heinonline.org/HOL/Page?handle=hein.journals/ylr93&div=24&collection=journals&set_as_cursor=41&men_tab=srchresults | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140706170727/http://heinonline.org/HOL/Page?handle=hein.journals%2Fylr93&div=24&collection=journals&set_as_cursor=41&men_tab=srchresults | archivedate = 2014-07-06 }}</ref>。阿根廷坚称于1816年[[阿根廷独立|独立]]时从西班牙手中继承了群岛的主权，因此英国1833年的占领属于非法行为<ref name="RIS">{{cite web | url = http://www.cancilleria.gov.ar/es/la-cuestion-de-las-islas-malvinas | title = La Cuestión de las Islas Malvinas | author = Secretaría de Relaciones Exteriores | publisher = Ministerio de Relaciones Exteriores y Culto (República Argentina) | accessdate = 2014-07-23 | archivedate = 2014-07-04 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140704155811/http://cancilleria.gov.ar/es/la-cuestion-de-las-islas-malvinas }}</ref>。

2009年，英国首相[[戈登·布朗|戈登·布朗]]与阿根廷总统[[克里斯蒂娜·费尔南德斯·德基什内尔|克里斯蒂娜·费尔南德斯·德基什内尔]]举行会晤，他表示不会再对福克兰群岛的主权问题作进一步蹉商<ref>{{cite news | url = http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/uk_news/politics/7969463.stm | title = No talks on Falklands, says Brown | newspaper = BBC News | publisher = British Broadcasting Corporation | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131103154618/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/uk_news/politics/7969463.stm | date = 2009-03-28 | accessdate = 2014-07-23 | archivedate = 2013-11-03 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。2013年3月，福克兰群岛针对其政治地位举行了{{link-en|2013年福克兰群岛主权公投|Falkland Islands sovereignty referendum, 2013}}，99.8%的选民支持群岛继续作为英国海外领土<ref>{{cite news | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131224073420/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-21731760 | archivedate = 2013-12-24 | url = http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-21731760 | title = Falklands referendum: Islanders vote on British status | newspaper = BBC News | publisher = British Broadcasting Corporation | date = 2013-03-10 | accessdate = 2014-07-23 | deadurl = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | archivedate = 2013-12-03 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131203053447/http://www.reuters.com/article/2013/03/12/us-falklands-referendum-idUSBRE92B02T20130312 | url = http://www.reuters.com/article/2013/03/12/us-falklands-referendum-idUSBRE92B02T20130312 | author = Marcos Brindicci and Juan Bustamante | title = Falkland Islanders vote overwhelmingly to keep British rule | publisher = Reuters | date = 2013-03-12 | accessdate = 2014-07-23 }}</ref>。阿根廷拒绝接受福克兰群岛加入谈判<ref>{{cite news | archivedate = 2014-02-02 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140202092439/http://en.mercopress.com/2013/01/31/timerman-rejects-meeting-falklands-representatives-only-interested-in-bilateral-round-with-hague | url = http://en.mercopress.com/2013/01/31/timerman-rejects-meeting-falklands-representatives-only-interested-in-bilateral-round-with-hague | title = Timerman rejects meeting Falklands representatives; only interested in 'bilateral round' with Hague | newspaper = MercoPress | date = 2013-01-31 | accessdate = 2014-07-23 }}</ref>，并且也不接受群岛上的公投结果<ref>{{cite news | author = Laura Smith-Spark | url = http://edition.cnn.com/2013/03/10/world/americas/falklands-referendum/ | title = Falkland Islands hold referendum on disputed status | publisher = CNN | date = 2013-03-11 | accessdate = 2014-07-23 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130529234448/http://edition.cnn.com/2013/03/10/world/americas/falklands-referendum | archivedate = 2013-05-29 | deadurl = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title=中方重申支持阿根廷马岛主权要求|url=https://world.huanqiu.com/article/46imBpxSn9p}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title=批准英国军机飞往马岛，巴西称对阿根廷的支持不影响巴英关系 |url=https://www.sohu.com/a/521548147_120244154}}</ref>。
